flowchart TD
    Start(( )) --> created

    created -->|install| installing
    created -->|start| starting
    created --> deleted

    installing -->|completed| stopped
    installing -->|start| starting
    installing --> deleted

    stopped -->|start| starting
    stopped --> deleted

    starting -->|booted| running
    starting -->|from save| paused

    running -->|stop| stopping
    running -->|pause| pausing

    stopping -->|done| stopped

    pausing -->|paused| paused

    paused -->|resume| resuming
    paused -->|restart| starting
    paused -->|stop| stopping

    resuming -->|running| running

    error -->|retry install| created
    error -->|recover runtime| stopped
    error --> deleted

    deleted --> End(( ))

    style Start fill:#e8611a,stroke:#e8611a
    style End fill:#e8611a,stroke:#e8611a
    style error fill:#3a1010,stroke:#e8611a
    style deleted fill:#1a1d28,stroke:#666
